Strong knowledge of the French and international media landscape.
Taste for business analytics and market research, combined with a curiosity for technology and innovation. Always eager to learn by discovering inspiring people and new concepts.
Above all, I am a genuine, cheerful and engaging person having fun in what I do, and considering work and teams as a source of fulfillment (among others).

